Print a TINC object to screen

Source: R/S3_methods.R
print.tin_obj.Rd

Print a TINC object to screen

# S3 method for tin_obj
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A TINC analysis computed with autofit.

...

Extra S3 parameters

Value

Nothing.

Examples

# Automatic call
rt = random_TIN()
